## Step 4: User Segmentation

| Primary Segment | Sub-segments | Key Needs / Use Cases | User Problems |
|-----------------|--------------|-----------------------|---------------|
| **Level Designers** | - Balance Specialists<br>- Content Creators<br>- LiveOps Tuning | - Coordinate mapping.<br>- Visualizing loot distribution.<br>- Analyzing storm deaths. | **Hypothesis**: Designers find it hard to see "Dead Zones" because paths overlap noise. |
| **AI Engineers** | - Bot Logic Devs<br>- QA Testers | - Bot pathing visualization.<br>- Behavior comparison vs humans. | **Hypothesis**: Engineers can't tell if a bot is "stuck" without seeing the 3D -> 2D mapping. |

